    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you started? This vehicle is in poor condition and definitely shows its age with significant wear and tear, but it offers a great opportunity for someone looking for a fixer-upper at a bargain price! It's an honest car with potential for the right owner who doesn't mind giving it some much-needed TLC.",
