    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine starts up without hesitation and the transmission provides smooth, reliable shifting across all gears. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal use, such as small stone chips on the hood, the paint still retains a healthy shine. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of any major wear or odors, making it a comfortable and dependable choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 36800.0,
