    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, offering a rare opportunity to own a car that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with no chips or imperfections, and the interior is pristine, still retaining that new-car smell with zero wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a full service history and every component functioning exactly as intended. This is a collector-quality example that has been meticulously garage-kept and pampered throughout its life.",
