      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an exacting standard, it presents in showroom condition with an unblemished exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance and total reliability. For the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising quality, this offering stands as a definitive testament to meticulous stewardship.",
      "price": 46500.0,
